      "seed": 1419295853,
      "version": 1227,
      "versionNonce": 1648984739,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776723002149,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Problem\n- Design a web crawler to extract text data from web and store it to LLM\n- Your crawler can run for only 5 days\n\nFunctional Requirements\n- Crawl the full web starting from seed urls\n- Extract text data and store\n\nScale\n - 10B Web page\n - 2 MB per page\n - 5 days to scrape\n- Unlimited resources\n\n\nNon-functional requirements (Constraints system must operate under)\n- Fault tolerant => handle failures gracefully\n- Politeness => don't DDOS site\n- Scalability => >= 10B pages\n- Efficiency => Crawl under 5 days\n \n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Problem\n- Design a web crawler to extract text data from web and store it to LLM\n- Your crawler can run for only 5 days\n\nFunctional Requirements\n- Crawl the full web starting from seed urls\n- Extract text data and store\n\nScale\n - 10B Web page\n - 2 MB per page\n - 5 days to scrape\n- Unlimited resources\n\n\nNon-functional requirements (Constraints system must operate under)\n- Fault tolerant => handle failures gracefully\n- Politeness => don't DDOS site\n- Scalability => >= 10B pages\n- Efficiency => Crawl under 5 days\n \n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "y2R0Xj3tL2TVOT6XXPffi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1030.846426862578,
      "y": 14.882817233871947,
      "width": 514.099609375,
      "height": 400,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a2",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1767741475,
      "version": 630,
      "versionNonce": 1461929699,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776724086977,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Core Entities\n- Text Data\n- URL metadata\n- Domain metadata\n\nAPI / Interface\n- input: set of seed urls\n- output: text data \n\nData Flow => High level process\n1. Take seed urls from frontier and IP from DNS\n2. Fetch HTML\n3. Extract text from HTML\n4. Store that text in db\n5. Extract Urls in text and add to frontier\n6. Repeat steps 1-5 until all URLs have been crawled",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Core Entities\n- Text Data\n- URL metadata\n- Domain metadata\n\nAPI / Interface\n- input: set of seed urls\n- output: text data \n\nData Flow => High level process\n1. Take seed urls from frontier and IP from DNS\n2. Fetch HTML\n3. Extract text from HTML\n4. Store that text in db\n5. Extract Urls in text and add to frontier\n6. Repeat steps 1-5 until all URLs have been crawled",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
